descriptionMarkdown:
🌟 Hey everyone, I’m Cloudiboy! 🌟

Today I want to show you my Research Lab, which currently produces for me around 4,000 science packs per minute! 🧪⚙️
But don’t worry – this thing can handle a lot more (around 9.000 science / min) … or can be scaled down if you prefer a more relaxed setup. 😎
It doesn’t have to run on Legendary – but it’s definitely ready if you are! 💪🔥

🔍 What makes it special?

💡 One really cool feature is the percentage-based display for the science packs!
This way, you can see at a glance how well your system is running. 📊🔬

👉 Important: For this to work properly, NO other science packs should be stored anywhere else in the logistics network. Otherwise, the percentage values will be off! ❌📦

🔧 If you change something...

If you adjust the amount of science packs, make sure to also update the calculators that convert those amounts into percentages.
🎯 Otherwise, things might get a bit weird… and nobody wants that, right? 😉

🎁 And now?

I hope some of you find this setup useful – or just cool 😄
Maybe it’ll help you out or inspire your own version! 🚀

Best wishes & have fun,
Your Cloudiboy 👋🙂
title: 9k science / min
